{"tid":10794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港摩天輪12月2至5日推半價優惠 yes!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T07:02:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd597110f5ac4a15a732b551c480621db7eca5c","tid":10794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/295944/xlarge/0e12238d1a60c66f4897154cb60260e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F295944%2Fxlarge%2F0e12238d1a60c66f4897154cb60260e8.jpg&h=b8ff8345&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n座落於中環新海濱的香港摩天輪為慶祝開幕兩周年，將於下個月2日至5日推出特別優惠，凡出示香港身份證即可獲門票半價優惠。 <br />\n<br />\n享用優惠後，成人門票為50元，小童及本地學生票價為35元，長者及殘疾人士為25元，而3歲以下兒童則為免費。優惠同樣適用於包廂門票，二至三人包廂由500元減至250元，四至八人包廂由800元減至400元。另外，優惠首兩日（2日及3日）摩天輪亦會延長開放時間至午夜12時，而4日及5日則開放至晚上11時。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/56873/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%BC%AA12%E6%9C%882%E8%87%B35%E6%97%A5%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%8A%E5%83%B9%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%88%E7%94%A8%E5%BE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F56873%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2591%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25BC%25AA12%25E6%259C%25882%25E8%2587%25B35%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2584%25AA%25E6%2583%25A0-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%2588%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BE%2597&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ecaec1d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/56873/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%BC%AA12%E6%9C%882%E8%87%B35%E6%97%A5%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%8A%E5%83%B9%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%88%E7%94%A8%E5%BE%97</a>"},{"pid":"fd430f2d2b57c37dce7c3dff63dbef188ec58d12","tid":10794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset